  "title": "连接 WLAN 成功后经常自动断开，如何解决？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  连接 WLAN 成功后，请保持在 WLAN 热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  若在有效距离内仍然会出现自动断开的情况，可能是由于手机与提供热点的路由器不兼容。请重启 WLAN 开关或重启路由器。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  在 WLAN 设置界面，点击![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171708237001.gif) > **高级**，然后点击**在休眠状态下保持**** WLAN ****连接**，打开选项菜单，选择**始终**。手机将始终保持与 WLAN 网络的连接。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171708385002.gif)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"> </p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</p>",
